<br>
Unfortunately I don't know how to raise faction with them.<br>
<br>
My other note: if you are a dark elf blacksmith and you get indifferent with Freeport merchants and militia, then you can do all your smithing in E Freeport.  It's better than Neriak because it has metal sheets for sale, whereas you have to make them from ore in Neriak.  Saves a lot of time in the long run.<br>
<br>
